-- Marsh & McLennan Names La Roche, Yost to Board of Directors
-- B y   A n d r e a   L u d t k e
-- 2012-01-18T14:24:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/marsh-mclennan-names-la-roche-yost-to-board-of-directors.html
Marsh & McLennan Cos., the second-
largest insurance broker, said Elaine La Roche and R. David Yost
have joined the board of directors.  La Roche, 62, is a senior adviser to China International
Capital Corporation U.S., and Yost, 64, was chief executive
officer of AmerisourceBergen Corp., New York-based Marsh &
McLennan said today in a statement distributed by  Business Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Ludtke in New York at 
 aludtke@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  